{"comments":"FontSource - where fonts come from and how to load them.\n\nFonts fall into two categories:\n\n**System Fonts** — Pre-installed on user devices, no loading required.\nThese are enumerable (finite set of well-known fonts).\n\n**Custom Fonts** — Require loading via @font-face, Google Fonts, Adobe\nFonts, or self-hosting. Infinite possibilities, need import config.\n\nThis distinction matters for:\n- Build-time optimization (system fonts need no assets)\n- Fallback strategies (custom fonts need loading states)\n- Brand validation (can we guarantee this font renders?)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontSource"],"SystemFont"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[71,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontSource.purs","start":[71,3]},"title":"System"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontSource"],"CustomFont"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontSource.purs","start":[72,3]},"title":"Custom"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontSource"],"FontSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[74,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/FontSource.purs","start":[74,1]},"title":"eqFontSource"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","FontSource"],"FontSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"ta